    "For children, we focus on \"edutainment\", combining education with entertainment through engaging games and activities that include visual and auditory elements.",
    "Our APP features video tutorials, interactive leanings, and comprehensive educational resources, catering to the diverse learning styles and needs of our users.",
    "For CODAs, the APP can also assist in teaching pronunciation, compensating for the lack of vocal language education in their families.We then develop our Interactive Auslan Communication at Home (IACH) APP tackling these user requirements with three main functions as shown in Fig. 1, including Text-to-Sign Lookup, Sign-to-Text Translation and Self-Teaching, respectively.",
    "Text-to-sign lookupWe offer the function that allows users to input an English word and present the corresponding Auslan gloss demonstrations.",
    "To support this text-to-sign lookup feature, we construct a comprehensive database linking textual words with relevant Auslan demonstration videos."
